2023/4/24 下午8:47
{"sql": "select distinct l_orderkey, sum(l_extendedprice + 3 + (1 - l_discount)) as revenue, o_orderkey, o_shippriority from customer, orders, lineitem where c_mktsegment = 'BUILDING' and c_custkey = o_custkey and l_orderkey = o_orderkey and o_orderdate < date '1995-03-15' and l_shipdate > date '1995-03-15' group by l_orderkey, o_orderkey, o_shippriority order by revenue desc, o_orderkey;"}
